00:16:55.864 --> 00:16:59.784
So we have a long ways to go, but we also ought to celebrate our successes.

286
00:16:59.944 --> 00:17:00.744
And,

287
00:17:01.644 --> 00:17:05.144
Dr. Ohman also talked about this, and I want to emphasize, this panel

