1739
01:35:44.150 --> 01:35:48.030
money. And they set up systems which allowed them to use it that way.

1740
01:35:48.310 --> 01:35:51.010
That was maybe one or two states, California being one of them.

1741
01:35:51.870 --> 01:35:55.729
But most of the other states didn't set up any good regulations at all.

1742
01:35:55.850 --> 01:35:59.130
So that money is just being used for a variety of other things.

1743
01:35:59.210 --> 01:36:03.110
So I guess my point is, it's a lot more work for us as a scientific

1744
01:36:03.150 --> 01:36:06.450
